## Best Practices

### Campaign Organization

1. **Use descriptive names** - Clear campaign identification
1. **Set date ranges** - Define campaign timeline
1. **Add descriptions** - Document campaign purpose
1. **Use statuses properly** - Keep campaign states current

### Data Management

1. **Import addresses early** - Set up before starting
1. **Define zones** - Organize geographically
1. **Configure sale model** - Set up workflow before sales begin

